又一齊周圍去<br />\n如果可以返去以前 我一定會揀返去同你哋一齊嘅時間<br />\n好好維持我哋嘅友誼 我哋嘅關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但一切都係如果<br />\n人大咗就愈嚟愈明珍惜依個道理<br />\n所以大家都要好好珍惜自己嘅身邊人<br />\n唔好令自己後悔<br />\n唔好令到自己冇咗段想維持一世嘅關係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T15:08:58.000Z","msg":"好有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係有啲野都吾係自己可以控制到就算啦<br />\n人越大就明白一切都冇得翻轉頭<br />\nLet it go<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n往事有啲不堪回首 有啲就只能回味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T15:33:08.000Z","msg":"係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我都只可以透過依個平台表達吓自己嘅諗法<br />\n當係懷念過去嘅一重渠道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3a49fef7b585bdca7582908c0d0f5f53578bc4","tid":591421,"uid":139828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T15:33:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1295f873f36e60bca3754c8a2c621eac9982105c","tid":591421,"uid":2479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cab2106a95ca9ee34dfed2b7841527b30efbcf21","tid":591421,"uid":135293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔會<br />\n諗返起佢d仆街嘢就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>咁好好彩<br />\n我嗰啲朋友都無對我做過啲咩仆街事<br />\n同佢嘅相識當係俾自己一個認清嗰個人嘅機會吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>見到依個post 我居然唔係因為曾經最好嘅朋友而唔開心 好諷刺<br />\n不過我都有錯 錯在居然投資青春比個條友而唔係放自己身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本放係自己身上有意義好多</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201